JOINT COMMISSION<br />AT<br />SETTING OF CAPSTONE.<br /> <br />
CHESTER A. ARTHUR.<br />W. W. CORCORAN, Chairman.<br />
M. E. BELL.<br />EDWARD CLARK.<br />JOHN NEWTON.<br />
Act of August 2, 1876.</td>

<td style="text-align: center;">
CORNER STONE LAID ON BED OF FOUNDATION<br />
JULY 4, 1848.<br /> <br />
FIRST STONE AT HEIGHT OF 152 FEET LAID<br />AUGUST 7, 1880.<br /> <br />
CAPSTONE SET DECEMBER 6, 1884.</td>

<td style="text-align: center;">
